de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.communication.wpsclient

Class WpsResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.communication.wpsclient.WpsResponse

  • public class WpsResponse
extends Object
    Present the response of a wps server. Contains the full response in responseBody and the response Time. In addtion it contains possible exceptions at execute Time of the specific request.
    Author:
    Florian Vogelpohl
